We Develop

Biomimetic Peptides that manage Plant Genetic

Discover miPEPs:

A Natural Solution to Control Plant Development

NATURAL PLANT MOLECULES ...

... REGULATING MICRORNA EXPRESSION ...

... AND Orchestrating PLANT Gene Expression

Technology assets

Crop Specific

   Because miPEPs are strictly specific to each plant, they do not have
   any action on other plants or other living organisms: a miPEP improving
   maize seed germination will not make weeds grow quicker.

Gene and Target Specific

   miPEP are also specific to their target gene: a miPEP with an effect on
   germination will not have another effect on flowering. This enable us
   to design very specific products targeting highly specific plant
   process.

Temporary

   The effect of our miPEPs on plant are only temporary: we simply give
   plants a boost at the right time but we leave their DNA intact.

Biodegradable

   miPEP are natural peptides that, unlike chemicals, can be easily
   degradable by the soil flaura and fauna, leaving no trace in the
   environment after a few days.

Application domains

Smart Biostimulants

Natural defense system booster

   Application domains

Specific Bioherbicide

Bioproduction of high value molecules

